<sec>
<st>
Biography</st>

<p>

John Joseph DeRoss was born in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../384/47384.xml">
Brooklyn, New York</link> to first generation immigrants from <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../061/25061.xml">
Piedmont</link>, <system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<economy wordnetid="108366753" confidence="0.8">
<group wordnetid="100031264" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../532/14532.xml">
Italy</link></group>
</economy>
</system>
. John is the nephew of Alphonse Persico Sr. and the father of Colombo crime family capo <link>
Jack J. DeRoss</link> born <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../852/8852.xml">
December 13</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../691/34691.xml">
1966</link> and mob associate Jamie T. DeRoss <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../586/20586.xml">
March 29</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../748/34748.xml">
1971</link> in <link>
Staten Island, New York</link>. He is a cousin of Carmine Persico and <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.8">
<superior wordnetid="110676018" confidence="0.8">
<principal wordnetid="110474950" confidence="0.8">
